    "updated_at": "2016-08-10T20:00:51Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "@sgallagher good to know that the policy has changed.  I'm aware of the reasons for wanting libraries to be unbundled, but the issue that we had already discussed to death was that the upstream author of these otherwise excellent libraries is explicitly against unbundled use.  This then leads to situations like this PR where some feel the only way forward is to hard-fork the libraries for the sole purpose of being able to sidestep the unbundling rules.\n"
  },
